    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_54_908-933",
      "chapterUid": 54,
      "range": "908-933",
      "markText": "“我们看见的不仅是一个海角，而且是一个新的世界！”",
      "totalCount": 1134,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=54&rangeStart=908&rangeEnd=933",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=54&rangeStart=908&rangeEnd=933"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_57_3883-3927",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "3883-3927",
      "markText": "种种事例表明，阿富汗这片土地并非不可征服，只是所有成功的征服者现在都被称为“阿富汗人”。",
      "totalCount": 1092,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=3883&rangeEnd=3927",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=3883&rangeEnd=3927"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_60_11206-11241",
      "chapterUid": 60,
      "range": "11206-11241",
      "markText": "诚如阿富汗的一则谚语所言：“院子里的一条好狗，比首都的好国王更有用。”",
      "totalCount": 1008,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=60&rangeStart=11206&rangeEnd=11241",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=60&rangeStart=11206&rangeEnd=11241"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_63_9177-9241",
      "chapterUid": 63,
      "range": "9177-9241",
      "markText": "具有讽刺意味的是，信件的内容不仅激怒了名单上的酋长，也激怒了那些未列入名单的酋长，因为他们被排除在外，意味着康诺利不认可其实力。",
      "totalCount": 910,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=63&rangeStart=9177&rangeEnd=9241",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=63&rangeStart=9177&rangeEnd=9241"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_57_496-565",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "496-565",
      "markText": "奇怪的是，每一次干涉，仿佛都出自同样的原因；每一次外敌来犯，也都延续着一贯的套路——汹汹而来、悻悻而走，似乎都不知道前车之覆乃是后车之鉴。",
      "totalCount": 901,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=496&rangeEnd=565",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=496&rangeEnd=565"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_71_1734-1817",
      "chapterUid": 71,
      "range": "1734-1817",
      "markText": "阿曼努拉的新法规定，罩袍不再是女性外出的必穿衣物，男人也无权要求她们穿戴。即便是丈夫也无权要求妻子穿戴。如果女性愿意穿着，法律不会干涉。这样的规定，简直就像一场革命。",
      "totalCount": 855,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=71&rangeStart=1734&rangeEnd=1817",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=71&rangeStart=1734&rangeEnd=1817"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_62_11017-11083",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "11017-11083",
      "markText": "《西姆拉宣言》中的内容还会反复被提及：英国人来阿富汗并非为了征服，而是“为了确保阿富汗独立与领土完整”。使命一旦完成，英军就会撤离。",
      "totalCount": 825,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=11017&rangeEnd=11083",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=11017&rangeEnd=11083"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_82_5919-6086",
      "chapterUid": 82,
      "range": "5919-6086",
      "markText": "事实证明，马苏德在军事方面天资卓越，几乎能和切·格瓦拉、毛泽东相提并论。",
      "totalCount": 803,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=82&rangeStart=5919&rangeEnd=6086",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=82&rangeStart=5919&rangeEnd=6086"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_59_4571-4628",
      "chapterUid": 59,
      "range": "4571-4628",
      "markText": "权力的秘密总在折磨入侵的外敌，他们总在扶植傀儡，试图达到代治的目的，却浑然不知一个官位在阿富汗并不代表相应的权力。",
      "totalCount": 784,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=4571&rangeEnd=4628",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=59&rangeStart=4571&rangeEnd=4628"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_60_2733-2812",
      "chapterUid": 60,
      "range": "2733-2812",
      "markText": "从某种意义上而言，阿富汗农村才是真正的阿富汗。了解乡村地区的社会结构，才能了解阿富汗的过去与未来。迄今为止，乡村地区的种种事态，仍在影响着这个国家的政治走向。",
      "totalCount": 756,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=60&rangeStart=2733&rangeEnd=2812",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=60&rangeStart=2733&rangeEnd=2812"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_75_5520-5570",
      "chapterUid": 75,
      "range": "5520-5570",
      "markText": "教育是文化，文化是意识形态。在阿富汗，苏联人花费的真金白银远远超过美国，却失去了阿富汗人的心和思想。",
      "totalCount": 756,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=75&rangeStart=5520&rangeEnd=5570",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=75&rangeStart=5520&rangeEnd=5570"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_90_9520-9601",
      "chapterUid": 90,
      "range": "9520-9601",
      "markText": "战争好似一把筛子，无用的品质将被残酷洗刷。战场中的人往往没有同情心，也不会拥有什么骑士精神。唯有毫不顾忌地行使暴力、破坏社会秩序的人，才能在无序的社会中赢得先机。",
      "totalCount": 648,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=90&rangeStart=9520&rangeEnd=9601",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=90&rangeStart=9520&rangeEnd=9601"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_72_6959-7057",
      "chapterUid": 72,
      "range": "6959-7057",
      "markText": "就在那个时候，会场里响起了（似乎是自愿的）请纳迪尔为王的呼声，他们恳请纳迪尔接受王冠。纳迪尔一再表示婉拒，但第三次呼声响起时，他说，自己将服从国家的意志，心怀谦卑地接下国家元首与绝对统治者的重担。",
      "totalCount": 624,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=72&rangeStart=6959&rangeEnd=7057",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=72&rangeStart=6959&rangeEnd=7057"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_56_907-955",
      "chapterUid": 56,
      "range": "907-955",
      "markText": "安萨利认为，阿富汗得以维持统一的原因之一是：外部的干涉和入侵，激发并一再刺激了阿富汗的国家认同。",
      "totalCount": 616,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=56&rangeStart=907&rangeEnd=955",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=56&rangeStart=907&rangeEnd=955"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_57_1277-1313",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "1277-1313",
      "markText": "美国能够控制城市，却无法平息那些自以为在捍卫伊斯兰教的人发起的农村叛乱。",
      "totalCount": 598,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=1277&rangeEnd=1313",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=1277&rangeEnd=1313"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_59_4763-4798",
      "chapterUid": 59,
      "range": "4763-4798",
      "markText": "伊斯兰教反对以物配主，他们认为摧毁偶像越是得力，就越能得到安拉的赐福。",
      "totalCount": 574,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=4763&rangeEnd=4798",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=59&rangeStart=4763&rangeEnd=4798"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_97_2584-2666",
      "chapterUid": 97,
      "range": "2584-2666",
      "markText": "迄今为止，中国政府未向阿富汗派出过一兵一卒，也没有在那里的军事行动上花过一分钱，然而，他们正在赢得阿富汗诸多矿藏资源的使用权，他们在那里缺乏军事存在正成为竞争优势。",
      "totalCount": 574,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24264355&chapterUid=97&rangeStart=2584&rangeEnd=2666",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00d32cc071723ea300ddf75?chapterUid=97&rangeStart=2584&rangeEnd=2666"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24264355_64_4966-5025",
      "chapterUid": 64,
      "range": "4966-5025",
      "markText": "阿富汗与其说是一个国家，不如说是一个家族企业；与其说是穆罕默德扎伊家族统治着这个国家，不如说他们才是这个国家的所有者。",
